node.text:
Charity Work (pt 3) I didn’t have many Nintendo games but we played Chip 'n Dale - Rescue Rangers to death. You could pick the other player up and render it incapacitated so naturally my sister and I would do that and try to throw the other one over a cliff or in the mouth of a mechanical dog😁 The ensuing rage was hard to match.

node.text:
Hand sanitizilla! ⭐️The Corona Diaries⭐️

When the pandemic hit last year I decided not to make that part of the comic. It would be very challenging to keep writing stories and be limited to real world restrictions, lockdowns, travel bans etc …! Also, I think comics are a great way to have a break and escape for a moment.

Having said that, I've made a special storyline where I explore some pandemic related stuff in the lives of the besties :) All Corona diaries available on Patreon.com/bestiethecomic

Thanks for being a patron!
